name: CoreAPI Connectivity_APIDesigner
description: API to access results of Planet 9 Connectivity_API Designer details.
about:
Description

Planet 9-APIDesigner facilitates to design the new API's using table definition or server script and by exporting API from an external system.

API Designer maintains the list of all API of the system.

You can use this API Connectivity_APIDesigner in your app if you want to get an API list, API details, delete the existing API, or create the new API. 

Every app must have the right roles (permissions) and authentication that enables access to the API Designer API.

Operations Performed 

List

Get the list of available API's. 

ResponseList - Definition

Get

Get the API details corresponding to the API Id.
